OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright day with sunny spells
OL,6,Fand scattered showers in the morning,
OL,7,Fbecoming largely dry with the best of
OL,8,Fthe sunnier spells in the afternoon.
OL,9,FOccasional strong and blustery winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLargely dry with some sunny
OL,12,Fspells at first. Becoming cloudier in
OL,13,Fthe west with the odd light shower,
OL,14,Fstaying dry with some clear spells in
OL,15,Fthe east. Winds gradually ease.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FMostly dry in the east with
OL,18,Fsunny spells and variable cloud.
OL,19,FCloudier in the west with a few light
OL,20,Fshowers. Some rain spreads east in the
OL,21,Fafternoon and evening. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
